{"tid":46722,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［打工撚］忍一時得寸進尺","createTime":"2016-12-20T00:07:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T02:02:37.000Z","uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9645d8a08a15a1129734264d85d84f3d2a1983fc","tid":46722,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:07:54.000Z","msg":"忍一時得寸進尺<br />\n退一步變本加厲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講小小背景 我係間大型公司到做designer 一開始係我唔好 唔適應公司個做野風格 又唔知上司想要咩 咁我做野都4 5年經驗 開個價都唔低 唔知係咪咁上司就好針對我 even比我知道佢同我同事話我人工唔值咁多 同同其他team大佬、老世背後話我討論我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我努力改進 有一排我覺得無論我幾努力都好 就算我知佢滿意我既野都好 佢都係會講d好難聽、好串既說話針對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢擺明係玩鳩我架啦 因為佢對其他同事完全係兩個樣 我未聽過佢會同其他同事咁串<br />\n<br />\n到做左個job格離team大佬讚我做得好 佢先對我冇咁串 以為可以繼續落去但原來佢一直mon住我 我做唔到佢要求佢就會不留情地話我、串我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一直諗 我忍左佢咁多次 比著其他人 會點？真心撚 你地會串返佢 會同佢傾 會黎個大反擊 會唔理繼續 忍 會辭職定點？"},{"pid":"60891f673a2d054838a54ccfff3641102cc74007","tid":46722,"uid":37758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:09:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>忍一時得寸進尺<br />\n退一步變本加厲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講小小背景 我係間大型公司到做designer 一開始係我唔好 唔適應公司個做野風格 又唔知上司想要咩 咁我做野都4 5年經驗 開個價都唔低 唔知係咪咁上司就好針對我 even比我知道佢同我同事話我人工唔值咁多 同同其他team大佬、老世背後話我討論我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n我努力改進 有一排我覺得無論我幾努力都好 就算我知佢滿意我既野都好 佢都係會講d好難聽、好串既說話針對我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢擺明係玩鳩我架啦 因為佢對其他同事完全係兩個樣 我未聽過佢會同其他同事咁串<br />\n<br />\n到做左個job格離team大佬讚我做得好 佢先對我冇咁串 以為可以繼續落去但原來佢一直mon住我 我做唔到佢要求佢就會不留情地話我、串我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一直諗 我忍左佢咁多次 比著其他人 會點？真心撚 你地會串返佢 會同佢傾 會黎個大反擊 會唔理繼續 忍 會辭職定點？</blockquote><br />\n繼續做<br />\n坐埋佢個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"008fd928fd0045f7bdd961849d8672ac0209bf71","tid":46722,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:09:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f132468e35757b49db9c32e99e01e6c467046694","tid":46722,"uid":27642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:10:42.000Z","msg":"佢係咪on9架<br />\nhr覺得o岩價咪請<br />\n關佢撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b6eeeea82b003ef9ff52cced67f77b762ccea32","tid":46722,"uid":15407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:17:41.000Z","msg":"應該係嫉妒你"},{"pid":"828b312594e22709907cf5ee12ce18fd6ae9cb5e","tid":46722,"uid":7775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:21:32.000Z","msg":"同上司關係唔好<br />\n做野起黎一定係比較吃力<br />\n依樣無得講<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一日喺度做咪唯有堅持<br />\n做好d比人睇 搏佢改觀<br />\n(雖然就咁睇好難<br />\n似係佢同時期經驗果陣無依個價，心理唔平衡)<br />\n<br />\n搵定工，有差不多待遇咪走"},{"pid":"867724b6bfbf022038dc6ed79f7c5cdb6238c9b2","tid":46722,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢係咪on9架<br />\nhr覺得o岩價咪請<br />\n關佢撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得好奇怪 我都做過幾間大公司 無一個上司會咁講野 唔講以為間公司係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過當初請我又冇經hr 佢同我老世見完直接請"},{"pid":"e721a477dfcbca464298260bbf0742ba9dc95b01","tid":46722,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係嫉妒你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會 我係小薯仔"},{"pid":"9710f0d920514674ec77948e6b58358ce2e0192f","tid":46722,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:35:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同上司關係唔好<br />\n做野起黎一定係比較吃力<br />\n依樣無得講<br />\n<br />\n我覺得一日喺度做咪唯有堅持<br />\n做好d比人睇 搏佢改觀<br />\n(雖然就咁睇好難<br />\n似係佢同時期經驗果陣無依個價，心理唔平衡)<br />\n<br />\n搵定工，有差不多待遇咪走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢改觀左啦 無咁串了 但一有小小野又會觸動到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430184c42537c033f444402d558ea743bb83d99f","tid":46722,"uid":648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:36:42.000Z","msg":"巴打 做開咩design?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48fde2d464e77d7085fad303d1a1493e1e906118","tid":46722,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T00:48:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 做開咩design?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔重要啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711d7bf582e5656e82bc3ef0aaf7a59ca6222fc1","tid":46722,"uid":9006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:51:08.000Z","msg":"未到最後都未知邊個輸贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1380113314cad9938fdf0837a4fdd5cb33a5387","tid":46722,"uid":28908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T01:58:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未到最後都未知邊個輸贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咩輸贏呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  忍得太多我驚我會有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  打工仔打份工 唔係打仗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd62ff88b1d210f193bd29cf0c172764faa7dae7","tid":46722,"uid":9006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T02:02:37.000Z","msg":"搵啲娛樂發洩一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}